    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251630/extras/606631a4f84fae58d6d2cfd971108668.poster.avif?t=1728980724\" width=615 height=353 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251630/extras/606631a4f84fae58d6d2cfd971108668.webm?t=1728980724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uprunner</strong> 是一款免费游玩的 MMO 垂直竞速游戏。赢得比赛或创建你自己的地图来赚取金币，并购买独特的随机生成的皮肤！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >演示功能</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有玩家都在同一张地图上，每5分钟更换一次！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含多个方块和皮肤的关卡编辑器（演示版包括8种方块类型）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >已有数百张社区地图可供游玩！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >登上排行榜，向世界展示你的技能！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受CS:GO 启发的独特皮肤生成系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过游戏解锁新的个人资料自定义元素！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于玩家交易的独特升级系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251630/extras/b3617d28e92f64d9726169b15d39ad2d.avif?t=1728980724\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251630/extras_big/b3617d28e92f64d9726169b15d39ad2d.avif?t=1728980724 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
